replace_text is three tools in one (pattern/replacement | edits[] | files[])
with required: [] because the forms are mutually exclusive — the schema no
longer says what a valid call looks like; agents learn by rejection. Splitting
the cross-file form (replace_in_files) lets each schema regain an honest
required list. Tension: more tools = bigger always-loaded surface; weigh
against the intent-shaped redesign task already on this list.


