stateful gotcha beside read-only ~occur~, and otherwise ~run_program~ territory.
Either drop it (lean on ~occur~ for orientation + ~run_program~ to navigate) or
fold a "move point to first match" option into ~occur~.

DONE: dropped the tool. Orientation = ~occur~ (read-only); moving point for a
follow-up edit = ~run_program~ (goto-char / re-search-forward). The lisp search
functions are unaffected.


